divs: Sighting Detailsme and my friend were walking down the road when i saw a saturn-like object at first i though it might be a blimp, it was rising form the horizon we watched it rise to atleast 1000 feet, suddenly it stopped and moved in our direction it maintained alitude it seemed to move as guided by intelligent force we then watched trying to figure out what it was we decided to try take a picture and go home, i grabbed my camera to get a picture and my friend took one with his phone, it did not appear in any of the pictures, i felt a feeling of excitement and intrigue as it passed by, i had a gut feeling this was not anything human. note: the craft was not by the airport

Summary: slightly saturn like, dark, unearthly texture and material
